# 🚀 GitHub DevOps Learning Lab

## 📌 Overview
This repository demonstrates core concepts of Git, GitHub, and DevOps automation using GitHub Actions.

It simulates a real-world workflow including:
- Branching
- Pull Requests
- CI/CD pipelines
- Docker image publishing (GHCR)

---

## 🎯 Objectives
- Learn Git workflow (commit, push, branches)
- Practice collaboration using Pull Requests
- Implement GitHub Actions workflows
- Automate Docker builds and deployment
- Understand CI/CD fundamentals

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- Git & GitHub
- GitHub Actions
- Docker
- HTML (sample app)

